); facility.getInitialProps = async function() { let nextToken = null; let results = []; let errors; let raw = {}; try { do { raw = await API.graphql( graphqlOperation(queries.listFacilitys, { limit: 10000, nextToken: nextToken }) ); nextToken = raw.data.listFacilitys.nextToken; raw.data.listFacilitys.items.map(value => results.push(value)); } while (nextToken); } catch (error) { errors = error; } return { data: results, errors: errors }; }; export default facility;
